" Filetype Terminal"{{{
augroup TerminalEnter
    autocmd!
    autocmd WinEnter term://* :startinsert
    autocmd TermOpen term://* :startinsert
    " autoresize terminal window
    autocmd WinLeave term://* :resize 3
    autocmd WinEnter term://* :resize 15
